{"id":124101,"type":6,"name":"三朵花","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/3b/eb/124101_P9e2H.jpg","summary":"　　琼瑶《六个梦》系列之一。 \r\n　　章家有着三个如花似玉的女儿，自小就接受章母严格的清规教育，严禁她们接近男子，宣扬世上所有的男人都是不值得信任的。大女儿章念琦（刘雪华 饰）与杨荫（张佩华 饰）相爱并私奔结婚，然而在母亲的阻挠下，杨荫的父母欺骗念琦杨荫早已结婚，这次只能算是重婚，遭受不住打击的念琦万念俱灰割脉自杀。二女儿念瑜（俞小凡 饰）对老师的崇拜由于母亲公开老师关心念瑜的信件，在学校引起轩然大波，念瑜在双重打击下精神出现问题。由于两个姐姐的悲惨遭遇，让母亲痛定思痛，放手让念琛（金素梅 饰）与恋人徐立群（徐乃麟 饰）远走高飞。 \r\n　　然而悲剧无法改变。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>三朵花</li><li><span>原作: </span><a href=\"/person/16898\">瓊瑤</a>《三朵花》</li><li><span>主演: </span><a href=\"/person/16659\">劉雪華</a> / 俞小凡 / 金素梅 / 張佩華 / 徐乃麟 / 羅吉鎮 / <a href=\"/person/16709\">李麗鳳</a></li><li><span>集数: </span>11</li><li><span>开始: </span>1990-04-11</li><li><span>结束: </span>1990-04-25</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>台灣</li><li><span>每集长: </span>50分钟</li><li><span>频道: </span>華視</li><li><span>导演: </span>鄭建榮</li><li><span>编剧: </span>林久愉</li>","eps":[{"id":476282,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/476282","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":476283,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/476283","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":476284,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/476284","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":476285,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/476285","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":476286,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/476286","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":476287,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/476287","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":476288,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/476288","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":476289,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/476289","type":0,"sort":8,"nam